g.text: Q1: I have friends available to me at work
Q2: I have one or more co-workers available who I talk to about day-to-day problems at work
Q3: I have co-workers available whom I can depend on when I have a problem
Q4: I have enough people available at work with whom I can talk about my job
Q5: I have people around me at work
Q6: I am well integrated with the department/company where I work
Q7: I am kept in the loop regarding company social events/functions
Q8: I am part of the company network
Q9: Upper management knows about my achievements
Q10: My supervisor communicates my achievements to upper management
